Branch will maintain, support, update, and provide error corrections for the Services to the same extent it does so for its customers generally. If Branch provides you with an update or maintenance release for the offline components of the Branch Services, unless you receive a separate license from Branch for that update or release that expressly supersedes these Terms, such update or release will be subject to these Terms. Branch shall have no liability for any damages that may result from Customer’s failure to implement upgrades or updates to the Services provided that Customer is notified in writing by Branch of such upgrade or update. All support requests must be sent to the Branch Support team via the “Submit a Ticket” function at
