(c) You further agree to obtain consent to your practices from your end users with regard to cookies and/or targeting and online behavioral advertising to the extent required by applicable laws, regulations, and self-regulatory guidelines. If you use Branch’s Engagement Builder feature, you agree to respect opt-out flags passed by Branch to you if you use Engagement Builder data for targeted advertisements. You acknowledge and agree that your use of the Services is subject to Branch’s Privacy Policy, located at
