Branch is committed to respecting and protecting the intellectual property rights of others and asks that you do the same. We will respond to notices of alleged copyright infringement that comply with applicable law. If you believe in good faith that any materials accessible on or from the Site infringe upon your copyright, you may request removal of those materials (or access thereto) from the Site by submitting written notification (a “
